42. Emotion & Story12:T457,These are compelling and converting online ads for a fundraiser on facebook. There is no monthly donations. Only one time donations.

VAR_UGC_SNAPCHAT = Make this ad seem like it was taken on snapchat with iphone quality (if text is on this ad turn it into snapchat font, if not text then just adjust the quality and feel to make it seem more snapchat/iphone organic
VAR_NATIVE_ORGANIC = Make this ad extremely native/organic as a normal community post regarding this fundraiser. It should not seem over the top and seem like it was took by someone trying to help and feel organic. 5% grain on the image.
VAR_HYPER_CLICKBAIT = Make the ad pop and make it super clickbaity. Super bold text if there is text. If not just distort the image and make it super bold/ eye catching. The main goal here is to make it scroll stopping not to try to convert right away just get clicks.
VAR_ADD_TEXT = Ensure there is text added in the ad
VAR_NO_TEXT = Ensure there is NO text added in the ad
